{"tid":605093,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"可以告訴我這樣是懷孕了嗎?","createTime":"2018-03-25T10:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T12:22:16.000Z","uid":1249,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"87fc45f87ab130ec21a50d8455a1dd2d781c0293","tid":605093,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"前2天與同男友親吻，他摸了乳房，我地2個有穿衣服，一直都有穿。壓在身上我發現他好像硬了。然後我地站起來，他說要解決，結果他打飛機。我不知道他有冇射了，可是有一點點白色的液體在我的裙子側面表面上。我衣服沒有脫，內褲也沒有脫，只是我有濕了，但沒有脫。我應該昨天來月經，可是到現在也沒有，我很怕懷孕了。可以告訴我這樣是懷孕了嗎?"},{"pid":"205e3d1c1d550f692ed2a8829c3839234ab09e04","tid":605093,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=760127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.beautyexchange.com.hk%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D760127&d=pA7LzFYulaAqKx0ipF9zeWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=011eeac1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=760127</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a3b20f7871f4dba1fbc50b121a5b911bd3b457","tid":605093,"uid":50779,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:46:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecfbf84d33d7744d6199d638efcec6673acac552","tid":605093,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:49:00.000Z","msg":"主主"},{"pid":"9fef739ba272c9020700692d2205ebbfdb035022","tid":605093,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:49:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"833aa4919c1d537f31fc267bd1ac380c4b3a96f5","tid":605093,"uid":156853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T11:00:35.000Z","msg":"一定係"},{"pid":"7e8af2742d79dca1994594eca30f74415fbcf549","tid":605093,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply